PEOPLE
v.
JORDAN S225848 Supreme Court of California August 17, 2016 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Werdegar, Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

The above-entitled matter is transferred to the Court of Appeal, Fourth Appellate District, Division One, with directions to vacate its decision and reconsider the cause in light of People v. Franklin (2016) 63 Cal.4th 261 , 283-284, 202 Cal.Rptr.3d 496 , 370 P.3d 1053 . (Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(d).)
